Class FESI.Data.ObjectPrototype 

FESI.Data.ESValue
   |
   +----FESI.Data.ESObject

public class ObjectPrototype
extends ESObject
Implements the prototype and is the class of all Object objects.

All functionality of objects is implemented in the superclass ESObject.

ObjectPrototype(ESObject, Evaluator)
Create a new Object with a specific prototype.

ObjectPrototype 
 public ObjectPrototype(ESObject prototype,
                        Evaluator evaluator)
Create a new Object with a specific prototype. This should be used by routine implementing object with another prototype than Object. To create an EcmaScript Object use ObjectObject.createObject()

Parameters:
prototype - the prototype of the new object
evaluator - The evaluator
